{"tid":2282853,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"XGU推出雙學位課程「理學士及研究碩士」，學生可於4年內取得學士及碩士學位","createTime":"2020-11-12T06:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T10:58:17.000Z","uid":240342,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2c85726a9fa432165bca25c6e5fea57c1a2ff362","tid":2282853,"uid":240342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港大學今日（11日）公布，理學院2021/22學年推出新雙學位課程「理學士及研究碩士（JS6688）」，學生可於4年內取得學士及碩士兩個學位，首年招收15至20名學生。理學院副院長（教學與學習）黃思齊稱，學生將會在理學院的頂尖科學家指導下接受個別科研指導，及早發展其對科研的興趣。<br />\n<br />\n黃思齊說，課程總修學分為303學分，理學士及研究碩士課程分別佔240及63學分。入讀該課程的學生首兩年會專注於理學士課程，學生可從7門精研主修科揀選主修。她續說，學生二年級的總成績平均積點（CGPA）須達3.6分才可繼績涵接至研究碩士課程。4年課程每年會收取本科學位課程學費4.2萬元，而研究碩士課程學費則由三年級起收取，總共12萬，即完成整個課程共要28.8萬元。黃思齊提到，校方將提供獎學金，支付研究碩士課程學費至少50％。<br />\n<br />\n理學院本科生入學事務總監張榮森稱，課程要求學生於中學文憑試（DSE）英文科取得5級成績，並必須修讀數學延伸部分M1或M2，以及兩門科學選修科。以4個核心科目加兩選修科及數學延伸部分計算，學生須至少於中學文憑試取得24分。他說，學院計劃首年招收15至20名學生，學位會從理學士課程（JS6901）調撥，沒有為聯招及非聯招生比例設限。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201111/s00001/1605077175478/%e6%b8%af%e5%a4%a7%e6%98%8e%e5%b9%b4%e6%8e%a8%e6%96%b0%e9%9b%99%e5%ad%b8%e4%bd%8d%e8%aa%b2%e7%a8%8b-4%e5%b9%b4%e4%bf%ae%e7%95%a2%e5%ad%b8%e5%a3%ab%e5%8f%8a%e7%a2%a9%e5%a3%ab%e5%ad%b8%e4%bd%8d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201111%2Fs00001%2F1605077175478%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e6%2598%258e%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e6%258e%25a8%25e6%2596%25b0%25e9%259b%2599%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e4%25bd%258d%25e8%25aa%25b2%25e7%25a8%258b-4%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e7%2595%25a2%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e5%25a3%25ab%25e5%258f%258a%25e7%25a2%25a9%25e5%25a3%25ab%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e4%25bd%258d&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=33eec81d\" data-ef-url=\